offset_right = 448.0
offset_bottom = 128.0
text = "How to Play

This is air hockey with a high voltage twist. 
Every time you hit the puck after your opponent, it transfers a charge 
to your paddle. If you accumulate too much energy, your paddle will 
overload, stunning you for 3 seconds.
To prevent an overload, touch the top or bottom rails to safely 
discharge. Be careful though : both overloading and discharging leaves 
your goal wide open for a brief moment.

First to 7 points wins.

Player 1: WASD, Player 2: Arrow keys
Press R to restart.

"
